    Whether you are visiting for dental tourism in Mexico or looking for a long-term dental solution, our services are designed to meet international standards with personalized care and modern technology.
    `,
    viewMore: "View Details",
    services: [
      {
        key: "dental_implants",
        title: "Dental implants",
        alt: "Dental implants in playa del carmen treatment",
        desc: "Permanent solutions to replace missing teeth with natural-looking results.",
        img: imgPathServicces + "Dental-implant.webp",
      },
      {
        key: "veneers",
        title: "Veneers",
        alt: "veneers in playa del carmen smile",
        desc: "Custom porcelain veneers designed to enhance your smile with long-lasting aesthetics.",
